  "title": "Facilities Coordinator cum admin 7094",
  "description": "<p>Working days: Monday - Friday 830am to 530pm</p><p>North East <br />Salary: $2,800 - $3200</p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Assist in office facilities and maintenance requirements by scheduling, assigning and follow up with vendor/contactors on work progress</li><li>Undertake and oversee office renovation projects and work with various vendors/ contractors to ensure completion</li><li>Assist in enhancing office efficiency by planning and implementing office systems, layouts, and safety equipment’s procurement</li><li>Recommend any improvements to reduce cost or increase efficiency of the facilities services</li><li>Responsible in the general office management like yearly carpet and office cleaning service</li><li>Assist with Building Management FSM to conduct and coordinate fire drill - CERT exercise</li><li>Support Production and Engineering departments on facilities maintenance, not limited to yearly disposal of expired chemical and damaged equipment under the compliance procedure</li><li>Track and update planned preventive maintenance schedule. Manage quarterly/ yearly renewal and compliance of necessary building and facilities permits and inspections</li><li>Organize and maintain proper facilities management documentation and records</li><li>Provide Office Admin support</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of relevant working experience</li><li>Proficient in MS Office software</li><li>Willing to do hands-on work such as packing, checking and organizing stock items</li></ul><p><br />Ho Ming Jie (Edmund) Reg No: R1987094 </p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279 </p>",
